    <item>
      <title>瑞银警告:美股大厂 AI 投资接近耗尽现金流,回报不及预期将回调</title>
      <link>https://bbyy11.github.io/ai-daily/archive-view.html?date=2026-05</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">ai-daily-n0604-16</guid>
